'''Avikam''' is one of the [[Lagoon languages]] of [[Ivory Coast]], spoken in Grand Lahou Département, Avikam Canton, South Department. It is a [[Kwa languages|Kwa language]], closely related to [[Alladian language|Alladian]], but other than that its position is unclear.

